-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository is designed to run with pre-trained ArcFace face-recognition
weights originally trained and distributed by the InsightFace project
(https://github.com/deepinsight/insightface), specifically the
`w600k_r50.onnx` model (IResNet-100 backbone).

The pre-calibrated INT8 form shipped here as `models/w600k_r50_ffw4.bin` is
a transformation of those InsightFace weights via the calibration pipeline
in this repository. Any use of these weights must comply with InsightFace's
model license -- see:

